erlunit: Start of Tests.
erlunit: + ok | Suite #1/Simple: Check for true | evaluates to true.
erlunit: + ok | Suite #1/Simple: Equality check | 1 == 1 as it should.
erlunit: + ok | Suite #1/Simple: Check for exception | runs into error, so fails as it should.
erlunit: Suite #2 gives names to individual checks
erlunit: + ok | Suite #2/Simple (verbose): One Equals One | evaluates to true.
erlunit: + ok | Suite #2/Simple (verbose): One Equals Zero | evaluates to false.
erlunit: + ok | Suite #2/Simple (verbose): One Does Not Equal Two | evaluates to false, not true, as it should.
erlunit: + ok | Suite #2/Simple (verbose): Foo Is Not True | evaluates to foo, not false, as it should.
erlunit: + ok | Suite #2/Simple (verbose): One Not Not Equals One | evaluates to true, not false, as it should.
